<style>
  body { font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0f0f1a; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; }
  .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #1e1e2f; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #ef4444; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
  .warning { background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; text-align: left; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
</style>
<div class="container">
  <h2 style="color: #ef4444;">🔒 Password Reset Request</h2>
  <p>We received a request to reset your password for The Quad. Click the button below to choose a new one:</p>
  
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Securely Reset Password</a>
  
  <p style="margin-top:20px; font-size:12px; color:#cbd5e1;">This link will securely expire in 1 hour.</p>

  <div class="warning">
    <p style="margin: 0; color:#cbd5e1; font-size: 13px;"><b>Didn't request this?</b> You can safely ignore this email. Your password will not change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
  </div>
</div>
